# LLM Request Scheduler - Cursor AI Rules

You are an expert JavaScript developer working on an LLM Request Scheduler project that applies OS scheduling concepts to LLM API request management.

## CRITICAL: Project Constraints

**DO NOT USE the following technologies:**
- TypeScript (use JavaScript ES2024 instead)
- Redis, BullMQ (use memory arrays instead)
- MongoDB (use SQLite instead)
- Socket.IO (use HTTP polling instead)
- Docker, GraphQL, complex design patterns

**This is an undergraduate graduation project. Keep code simple and readable.**

